import React from "react";
import { Navbar, Nav, Form, Button } from "react-bootstrap";

const NavBar = () => {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="light" variant="light" expand="lg" className="navbar-container">
      <Navbar.Brand style={{ color: "#f09819" }} href="/">
        Made In Sri Lanka
      </Navbar.Brand>
      <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
      <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
        <Nav className="ml-auto">
          <Form inline className="form-group my-1 mx-3">
            <Form.Control
              size="sm"
              type="text"
              placeholder="Search"
              className="mr-sm-2 search-input"
            />
            <Button
              variant="outline-secondary"
              size="sm"
              className="my-1 search-btn"
            >
              Search
            </Button>
          </Form>
          <Nav.Link href="/login" className="text-center">
            Login
          </Nav.Link>
          <Nav.Link href="/register" className="text-center">
            Register
          </Nav.Link>
        </Nav>
      </Navbar.Collapse>
    </Navbar>
  );
};

export default NavBar;
